dct_title_s: Cadastral map of property lines in Manasquan, section no. 2
dct_description_sm: This map surveys the coastal vicinity of the Manasquan River and Inlet. It includes detailed cadastral and property information around Meadow point. The map is made with color ink tracing and contains limited information. Date is unknown.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
